<Link id="l00657" /><CodeLine lineNumber="657"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// Emit the largest nop instruction smaller than or equal to \\p NumBytes</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00658" /><CodeLine lineNumber="658"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">/// bytes.  Return the size of nop emitted.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00659" /><CodeLine lineNumber="659" lineLink="#ab371721ad31c3a0d4e5eb8fce0e8a13a"><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">static</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">unsigned</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="#ab371721ad31c3a0d4e5eb8fce0e8a13a">emitNop</a>(<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mcstreamer">MCStreamer</a> &amp;OS, </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">unsigned</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> NumBytes,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00660" /><CodeLine lineNumber="660"><span class="doxyHighlight">                        </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">const</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/x86subtarget">X86Subtarget</a> &#42;Subtarget) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00661" /><CodeLine lineNumber="661"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Determine the longest nop which can be efficiently decoded for the given</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00662" /><CodeLine lineNumber="662"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// target cpu.  15-bytes is the longest single NOP instruction, but some</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00663" /><CodeLine lineNumber="663"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// platforms can&#39;t decode the longest forms efficiently.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00664" /><CodeLine lineNumber="664"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">unsigned</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> MaxNopLength = 1;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00665" /><CodeLine lineNumber="665"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Subtarget-&gt;is64Bit()) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00666" /><CodeLine lineNumber="666"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// FIXME: We can use NOOPL on 32-bit targets with FeatureNOPL, but the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00667" /><CodeLine lineNumber="667"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// IndexReg/BaseReg below need to be updated.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00668" /><CodeLine lineNumber="668"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Subtarget-&gt;hasFeature(X86::TuningFast7ByteNOP))</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00669" /><CodeLine lineNumber="669"><span class="doxyHighlight">      MaxNopLength = 7;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00670" /><CodeLine lineNumber="670"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Subtarget-&gt;hasFeature(X86::TuningFast15ByteNOP))</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00671" /><CodeLine lineNumber="671"><span class="doxyHighlight">      MaxNopLength = 15;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00672" /><CodeLine lineNumber="672"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Subtarget-&gt;hasFeature(X86::TuningFast11ByteNOP))</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00673" /><CodeLine lineNumber="673"><span class="doxyHighlight">      MaxNopLength = 11;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00674" /><CodeLine lineNumber="674"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00675" /><CodeLine lineNumber="675"><span class="doxyHighlight">      MaxNopLength = 10;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00676" /><CodeLine lineNumber="676"><span class="doxyHighlight">  &#125; </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Subtarget-&gt;is32Bit())</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00677" /><CodeLine lineNumber="677"><span class="doxyHighlight">    MaxNopLength = 2;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00678" /><CodeLine lineNumber="678"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00679" /><CodeLine lineNumber="679"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Cap a single nop emission at the profitable value for the target</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00680" /><CodeLine lineNumber="680"><span class="doxyHighlight">  NumBytes = std::min(NumBytes, MaxNopLength);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00681" /><CodeLine lineNumber="681"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00682" /><CodeLine lineNumber="682"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">unsigned</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> NopSize;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00683" /><CodeLine lineNumber="683"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">unsigned</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> Opc, BaseReg, ScaleVal, IndexReg, Displacement, SegmentReg;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00684" /><CodeLine lineNumber="684"><span class="doxyHighlight">  IndexReg = Displacement = SegmentReg = 0;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00685" /><CodeLine lineNumber="685"><span class="doxyHighlight">  BaseReg = X86::RAX;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00686" /><CodeLine lineNumber="686"><span class="doxyHighlight">  ScaleVal = 1;</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01105" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1105"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// We want to emit the following pattern, which follows the x86 calling</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01106" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1106"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// convention to prepare for the trampoline call to be patched in.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01107" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1107"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01108" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1108"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   .p2align 1, ...</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01109" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1109"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// .Lxray&#95;event&#95;sled&#95;N:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01110" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1110"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   jmp +N                        // jump across the instrumentation sled</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01111" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1111"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ...                           // set up arguments in register</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01112" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1112"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   callq &#95;&#95;xray&#95;CustomEvent@plt  // force dependency to symbol</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01114" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1114"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   &lt;jump here&gt;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01115" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1115"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01116" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1116"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// After patching, it would look something like:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01117" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1117"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01118" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1118"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   nopw (2-byte nop)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01119" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1119"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ...</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01120" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1120"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   callq &#95;&#95;xrayCustomEvent  // already lowered</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01121" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1121"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ...</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01122" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1122"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01123" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1123"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// ---</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01124" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1124"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// First we emit the label and the jump.</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01142" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1142"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Then we put the operands in the %rdi and %rsi registers. We spill the</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01203" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1203"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// We want to emit the following pattern, which follows the x86 calling</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01204" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1204"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// convention to prepare for the trampoline call to be patched in.</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01206" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1206"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   .p2align 1, ...</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01207" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1207"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// .Lxray&#95;event&#95;sled&#95;N:</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01210" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1210"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   callq &#95;&#95;xray&#95;TypedEvent@plt  // force dependency to symbol</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01211" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1211"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ...</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01213" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1213"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01214" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1214"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// After patching, it would look something like:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01215" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1215"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01216" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1216"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   nopw (2-byte nop)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01217" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1217"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   ...</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01218" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1218"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//   callq &#95;&#95;xrayTypedEvent  // already lowered</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01220" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1220"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01221" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1221"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// ---</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01240" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1240"><span class="doxyHighlight">  <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/transforms/lib/transforms/utils/mem2reg-cpp/#a6fde3eb6ca09ddf2fd76432176d817bb">Register</a> SrcRegs&#91;&#93; = &#123;0, 0, 0&#125;;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01241" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1241"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01242" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1242"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Then we put the operands in the SystemV registers. We spill the values in</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01243" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1243"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// the registers before we clobber them, and mark them as used in UsedMask.</span></CodeLine>
